<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>Verification account</title>
  </head>
  <body style="text-align: center; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #fefaeb">
    <header style="background: #fefaeb">
      <div style="padding-top: 35px">
        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/0nfNbwg/1.png" alt="LOGO" />
      </div>
    </header>
    <content>
      <div style="background: #fff; margin: 40px 25px 0; padding: 40px 50px">
        <p
          style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #252525; margin: 0"
        >
          Welcome to Limupa!
        </p>
        <p
          style="
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #252525;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 35px 0 5px;
          "
        >
          Hello &lt;name&gt;
        </p>
        <p
          style="
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #252525;
            margin: 0;
            max-width: 400px;
            display: inline-block;
          "
        >
          We know you’d love to access your results and manage your account. In
          order to do that, we just need you to confirm your email address and
          add a password via the link below.
        </p>
        <div style="padding: 30px 0">
          <button
            style="
              font-size: 14px;
              background: #fedd44;
              border: none;
              padding: 15px 60px;
              font-weight: bold;
              color: #000;
            "
          >
            COMPLETE MY ACCOUNT
          </button>
        </div>
        <p
          style="
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #252525;
            margin: 0;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            max-width: 250px;
            display: inline-block;
          "
        >
          Ignore this email if you didn’t request this as the link will expire
          in 1 hour.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #252525; margin: 0">
          If you’d like to get in touch, email us at
          <span style="font-weight: bold">info@limupa.com</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </content>
    <footer style="padding: 40px 0 30px">
      <span style="display: inline-block; margin-right: 7px">
        <img
          src="https://zestteedev.blob.core.windows.net/zestteedev/ig-icon-f5ef379e7b18f0b0.png"
          alt="IG"
        />
      </span>
      <span style="display: inline-block">
        <img
          src="https://zestteedev.blob.core.windows.net/zestteedev/fb-icon-c7f97d8e7ab11225.png"
          alt="FB"
        />
      </span>
      <p style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500">
        &copy; 2020 Limupa. All rights reserved
      </p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
